{"tid":2393243,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"(求解)43 south車厘子真假一問","createTime":"2021-02-03T10:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T01:13:53.000Z","uid":56896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"6cb0f1ea262309e3d778415f510a02979699b5b0","tid":2393243,"uid":56896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T10:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KawujTD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKawujTD.png&h=6eccad1f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTDP4kJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTDP4kJ.png&h=279af1e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5pbev0V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5pbev0V.png&h=1e67ed3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一次喺果欄買咗盒1公斤 43C south車厘子 （$250），但係返到去發現盒邊冇QR code可以追查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再查staccato品種上網又好似冇。請教有冇人知道呢盒野係咪假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定係我愚昧其實今年轉左用QR code之類追查源頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求有冇專家或者食開人士解答🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼<br />\n（利申：喺果欄一檔較大型同有規模嘅舖頭買）"},{"pid":"f166b1854160d4d2f102bf81795ceea552cf55fd","tid":2393243,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T10:28:44.000Z","msg":"個種有咗好多年<br />\n只係唔係出名最好食嘅種遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa